MOVIE TICKET BOOKING SYSTEM

1. Project Purpose
This software is a Movie Ticket Booking System designed to manage movie ticket reservations. 
The system enables users to browse movie schedules, select available seats, make bookings, 
and process payments. It demonstrates core concepts of object-oriented programming and 
real-world application workflows.

2. Modules
- user.ts - Manages user information and profile data.
- movieSchedule.ts - Handles movie details and schedule information.
- booking.ts - Manages ticket bookings and seat selection.
- payment.ts - Process payment transactions for bookings.

